data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting 1704 square feet of living space, located in a desirable neighborhood and just 3 years old. Crafted with exceptional quality and desirable finishes, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. The spacious open floor plan provides a seamless flow between the living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The Great Room is a highlight of this home, featuring high ceilings, an upgraded stone fireplace, and large windows that flood the room with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The kitchen gives you all the space you would need and features white shaker cabinets, a large island with breakfast bar, beautiful granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a grey subway tile backsplash. Enjoy the beautiful outdoors with not one, but two large covered porches - both front and back. These spaces provide the perfect setting for relaxation, morning coffee, or evening chats. The Master Bedroom is a tranquil retreat with a luxurious custom tile shower featuring a frameless shower door, adding a touch of sophistication and elegance. The home includes a spacious two-car garage, providing ample storage space and secure parking for your vehicles. The property boasts a privacy fence, offering seclusion and security for outdoor activities and gatherings. The thoughtful addition of a mud bench in the home adds practicality and organization, ideal for storing everyday essentials. The front and back yards are beautifully landscaped and come with a sprinkler system, ensuring easy maintenance and lush surroundings. The home is equipped with window blinds, making it move-in ready and allowing you to enjoy your privacy from day one. This home is located in a sought-after area, with an easy commute to RAFB and zoned for the prestigious VETERANS HIGH SCHOOL. Enjoy the convenience of nearby schools, parks, shopping centers, and easy access to major roadways, making your daily commute a breeze.  Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a quality-built home with desirable features and a great location. Schedule a viewing today and make this dream home yours!
